idea-plugin.change-notes:
10 Jan 2015: improvements and new inspections
<br /> 
<br /> - Updated several inspections description;
<br /> - Method name matches existing field name: resolved false-positives;
<br /> - Slow alter in foreach: improved unset analysis in nested loops;
<br /> - PhpUnit: resolved false-positives with assertNull;
<br /> - Badly organized exception handling: resolved false-positives caused by comments;
<br /> - Statement could be decoupled from foreach: resolved false-positives;
<br /> - Callable calls in loops termination condition: reporting re-worked;
<br /> - Non-optimal if conditions: recognize conditions with identical operands;
<br /> 
<br /> - Variable functions usage: implemented;
<br /> - Inconsistent 'http_build_query(...)' result: implemented;
<br /> - Exceptions handling and annotating: improved analysis, report possible issues in finally;
<br /> 
